name: 维克托·冈萨雷斯
name_full: 维克托·冈萨雷斯 Victor Gonzalez
introduction: Victor was born on June 13, 1975. He grew up in Elizabeth, New Jersey. He made his debut in entertainment as the lead vocalist/guitarist for the heavy metal band Ominous having five EP's and 2 Albums, releasing four music videos. He left the band in 2015 and in 2021 decided to pursue a new venture and dedicated himself to becoming an actor. He's achieved success in projects acting in films that include actors John Travolta, Bruce Willis and Austin Butler to name a few. He is an actor known Vindication season three, Moving Valentine, Marvel's Daredevil and Monsters: The Lyle and Erik Menendez story, on Netflix
